title: Comedian Ms Patt Jordan Cooper

description:
Today on the show we had friend to the room and comedian Ms Patt and her producer Jordan Cooper where they spoke about adapting Ms. Pat's True Story, Set Chemistry, Authenticity and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Corey Booker for his saterical comments on defunding the police and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
